Databricks


Databricks is a cloud-based data platform used for building, running, and managing:
    🚀 Big data processing
    🤖 Machine learning & AI workloads
    🛢️ Data engineering pipelines
    📊 Analytics & BI dashboards


It’s built on top of Apache Spark and provides a unified environment for teams to collaborate on data projects


